pair.value: AS EI Northrow Request and Retrieve Company Check Summary
PM to request and retrieve a Northrow Check Summary for a company
= #"_a-0000e329-3415-8000-9ba2-011c48011c48_352001"( pmName: pm!name, keyPvName: "Company ID", pvIdentifier: pv!companyId)

pv.name: companyCheckRequest
pv.expr: ='type!{urn:com:appian:types:AS:EI:NORTHROW}AS_EI_NORTHROW_CompanyCheckRequest'( company: 'type!{urn:com:appian:types:AS:EI}AS_EI_NORTHROW_Company'( name: "Acme Corp", registered: 'type!{urn:com:appian:types:AS:EI}AS_EI_NORTHROW_Address'(country: "US") ), header: 'type!{urn:com:appian:types:AS:EI}AS_EI_NORTHROW_Header'( transaction_reference: 1, remoteverify_enabled: true, profile_uuid: "d9e28487-7c9f-42a1-ad71-0e6bc5bb9bcd" ))

a:acp.name: expression
a:acp.a:expr: = or( and( pv!companyCheckResult.statusCode = #"_a-0000e539-6d59-8000-9bd0-011c48011c48_1253418", index(pv!companyCheckResult.body, "rag", null) = #"_a-0000e539-6d59-8000-9bd0-011c48011c48_1258447" ), and( pv!companyCheckResult.statusCode = #"_a-0000e539-6d59-8000-9bd0-011c48011c48_1259666", pv!retryCount = 0 ))

output-exprs.el: companyCheckSummary:#"_a-0000e539-6d59-8000-9bd0-011c48011c48_1235117"( response: pv!companyCheckResult, companyCheckSummary: pv!companyCheckSummary, isSuccess: pv!isCompanyCheckSuccess )

annotation.text: AS EI Northrow Request and Retrieve Company Check Summary

This process model is designed to retrieve customer check
1. Call AS_EI_NORTHROW_INT_createCompanyCheck integration which will return checkId 2. Call AS_EI_NORTHROW_INT_retrieveCompanyCheck using checkid which will return company check details 3. Company check integration is retried only if response code is 200 and RAG is waiting, or a 404 is observed on the first time to allow for a potential race condition where Northrow has not yet logged the checkUUID. Their support team has been notified of this race condition, and this condition should be removed once it is resolved. 4. Default process timeout is set using AS_EI_NORTHROW_DEFAULT_TIMEOUT which is 30 min
